<h3>Basics</h3>
<div>Set your site title, home card, and logo image:</div>
<blockquote>
<div>{{*title|bar;type:Phrase}}</div>
<div>{{*home|bar;type:Phrase}}</div>
<div>{{*logo|bar;type:Image}}</div>
<div>{{*main menu|bar}}</div>
</blockquote>
<h3>Cardtypes </h3>
<p> [[/new/cardtype|Add new Type]]</p>
<p>{{Cardtype+*type+by name|bar; title: all cardtypes}}</p>
<h3>Rules</h3>
<div>Cards are configured by creating <em>rules</em>.  </div>
<div> </div>
<h5>Webpage rules</h5>
<div>
<blockquote>{{*all|rules_table; filter:webpage}}</blockquote>
<h5>Permission rules</h5>
<blockquote>{{*all|rules_table; filter:permission}}</blockquote>
</div>
<div><em>[[http://decko.org/rules | More about rules.]]</em></div>
<div> </div>
<div>
<h3>Views</h3>
<p>You can try out different views below</p>
<p>{{Home+original|viewer}}</p>
</div>
